title: Swaziland - Credit Rating
description: Moody's credit rating for Swaziland was last set at B3 with stable outlook. In general, a credit rating is used by sovereign wealth funds, pension funds and other investors to gauge the credit worthiness of Swaziland thus having a big impact on the country's borrowing costs. This page includes the government debt credit rating for Swaziland as reported by major credit rating agencies.
